ons|authorlink=Richard Simmons|medium=[[Compact Cassette]]|publisher=[[Holtzbrinck Publishing Group#Subsidiaries and imprints|Audio Renaissance]]|location=[[Southfield, Michigan]]|year=1993|isbn=978-1559272193}}</ref>\n\n====Compact disc====\n* ''Richard Picks the Hits, Volume 1''\n* ''Richard Picks the Hits, Volume 2''\n* ''Country Cardio''\n* ''Oh Happy Day''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Richard-Simmons-Happy-Day-Simmons/dp/B000DGY0C0|title=Oh Happy Day|first=Richard|last=Simmons|authorlink=Richard Simmons|medium=[[Compact disc|Audio CD]]|work=[[Mood Media#Acquisitions|Somerset Entertainment]]|publisher=[[Mood Media]]|location=[[Austin, Texas]]|date=January 3, 2006|accessdate=March 7, 2017|asin=B000DGY0C0}}</ref>\n* ''Fitness Fiesta''\n* ''Wicked Workout''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Richard-Simmons-Wicked-Workout-Simmons/dp/B000DGY0CK|title=Wicked Workout|medium=[[Compact disc|Audio CD]]|date=January 3, 2006|work=[[Mood Media#Acquisitions|Somerset Entertainment]]|publisher=[[Mood Media]]|location=[[Austin, Texas]]|accessdate=March 8, 2017|asin=B000DGY0CK}}</ref>\n* ''Big Screen Burn''\n* ''Shimmy Into Shape''\n* ''In the Mood to Lose''\n* ''Classical Chillout''\n\n====Vinyl record====\n* ''Reach'' (Elektra Records, 1983)\n\n====Singles====\n* ''This Time'' (Elektra Records, 45 rpm 1983)\n\n====Digital compact cassette====\n* ''Colors of Your Life (single tape)'' (Goodtimes Entertainment, BASF 90 Min. 1998)\n{{Col-break}}\n\n===Visual media===\n====DVD====\n* \"Richard Simmons Project H.O.P.E. - Health, Optimism, Passion, Energy\"\n* ''Richard Simmons and the Silver Foxes''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Richard-Simmons-Silver-Foxes/dp/B0004Z32ME|title=Richard Simmons and the Silver Foxes|medium=[[DVD]]|work=[[Warner Home Video]]|publisher=[[Warner Bros.]]|location=[[Burbank, California]]|date=December 14, 2004|accessdate=March 8, 2017|asin=B0004Z32ME}}</ref>\n* ''Disco Sweat''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://ww