2QEP2|title=Sweatin' to the Oldies|medium=[[DVD]]|work=[[Time Life#Entertainment|Time Life Entertainment]]|publisher=[[Time Life]]|location=[[New York City]]|date=March 14, 2008|accessdate=March 8, 2017|asin=B001U2QEP2}}</ref>\n* ''Sweatin' to the Oldies 2''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Richard-Simmons-Sweatin-Oldies-Vol/dp/B0017HEYGG|title=Sweatin' to the Oldies 2|medium=[[DVD]]|work=[[Time Life#Entertainment|Time Life Entertainment]]|publisher=[[Time Life]]|location=[[New York City]]|date=June 3, 2008|accessdate=March 8, 2017|asin=B0017HEYGG}}</ref>\n* ''Sweatin' to the Oldies 3''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Richard-Simmons-Sweatin-Oldies-3/dp/B003RLNW3G|title=Sweatin' to the Oldies 3|medium=[[DVD]]|work=[[Time Life#Entertainment|Time Life Entertainment]]|publisher=[[Time Life]]|location=[[New York City]]|date=January 1, 2007|accessdate=March 8, 2017|asin=B003RLNW3G}}</ref>\n* ''Sweatin' to the Oldies 4''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Sweatin-Oldies-Vol-20-Years/dp/B000Z8H1ZE|title=Sweatin' to the Oldies 4|medium=[[DVD]]|work=[[Time Life#Entertainment|Time Life Entertainment]]|publisher=[[Time Life]]|location=[[New York City]]|date=April 9, 2013|accessdate=March 8, 2017|asin=B000Z8H1ZE}}</ref>\n* ''Sweatin' to the Oldies 5''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Sweatin-Oldies-5-Richard-Simmons/dp/B003KIAWOS|title=Sweatin' to the Oldies 5|medium=[[DVD]]|work=[[Time Life#Entertainment|Time Life Entertainment]]|publisher=[[Time Life]]|location=[[New York City]]|date=December 14, 2010|accessdate=March 8, 2017|asin=B003KIAWOS}}</ref>\n* ''Love Yourself and Win''\n* ''Boogie Down the Pounds''\n* ''Tonin' to the Oldies''\n\n====Video cassette====\n* ''Everyday with Richard Simmons''\n* ''The Stomach Formula''\n* ''Get Started''\n* ''Reach for Fitness - A Special Video of Exercises for the Physically Challenged''<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.amazon.com/Reach-Fitness-Exercises-Physically-Challenged/dp/B